				},
				"category": "offensive",
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>The Púca magically polymorphs into a humanoid or animal with a level equal to or less than its own that can be mounted, or back into its true form. It reverts to its true form if it dies. Any equipment it is wearing or carrying is absorbed or borne by the new form (the Púca’s choice).</p><hr /><p>@Localize[PF2E.NPC.Abilities.Glossary.ChangeShape]</p>",
